📱 Social Media Do’s and Don’ts Checklist
✅ Do’s
# Think before posting and ensure content is appropriate
# Protect your personal information and privacy
# Be respectful and polite in all interactions
# Verify information before sharing
# Use strong passwords and enable security settings
❌ Don’ts
# Don’t share sensitive or confidential information
# Don’t engage in cyberbullying or harassment
# Don’t spread fake or unverified news
# Don’t overshare personal life details
# Don’t click on suspicious links or unknown sources
